trans-unit.source: Represents a dictionary of custom data objects that you can associate with certain objects in the SharePoint tools object model.
trans-unit.target: 表示可与 SharePoint 工具对象模型中的某些对象相关联的自定义数据对象字典。

trans-unit.source: You can add custom data to instances of types in the SharePoint tools object model that implement the <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject> interface.
trans-unit.target: 你可以将自定义数据添加到实现 SharePoint 工具对象模型中的类型的实例<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject>接口。

trans-unit.source: These types have an <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject.Annotations%2A> property that returns an <xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotationDictionary> object.
trans-unit.target: 这些类型具有<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotatedObject.Annotations%2A>返回的属性<xref:Microsoft.VisualStudio.SharePoint.IAnnotationDictionary>对象。

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Associating Custom Data with SharePoint Tools Extensions](/visualstudio/sharepoint/associating-custom-data-with-sharepoint-tools-extensions.md).
trans-unit.target: 有关详细信息，请参阅[关联与 SharePoint 工具扩展的自定义数据](/visualstudio/sharepoint/associating-custom-data-with-sharepoint-tools-extensions.md)。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object to add.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的对象的类型。

trans-unit.source: This is the key of the object in the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 这是在字典中对象的键。

trans-unit.source: The object to add.
trans-unit.target: 要添加的对象。

trans-unit.source: Adds an object to the dictionary by using the <see cref="T:System.Type" /> of the object for the key.
trans-unit.target: 通过针对键使用对象的 <see cref="T:System.Type" />，将对象添加到字典中。

trans-unit.source: An object with the same type already exists in the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 字典中已存在具有相同类型的对象。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的对象的类型。

trans-unit.source: This is the key that is associated with the object.
trans-unit.target: 这是与对象相关联的密钥。

trans-unit.source: The type must be a reference type.
trans-unit.target: 类型必须是引用类型。

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that has the specified reference type.
trans-unit.target: 获取具有指定引用类型的对象。

trans-unit.source: The object associated with the specified key, if the key is found; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到指定键，则为指定键关联的对象；否则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的对象的类型。

trans-unit.source: The type must be a reference type.
trans-unit.target: 类型必须是引用类型。

trans-unit.source: The key of the object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的对象的键。

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that has the specified reference type and is associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 获取具有指定引用类型并与指定键相关联的对象。

trans-unit.source: The object associated with the specified key, if the key is found and the object has the type <paramref name="T" />; otherwise, <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果找到指定键，且对象具有类型 <paramref name="T" />，则为指定键关联的对象；否则为 <see langword="null" />。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object to remove.
trans-unit.target: 要移除的对象的类型。

trans-unit.source: This is the key that is associated with the object.
trans-unit.target: 这是与对象相关联的密钥。

trans-unit.source: Removes an object with the specified <see cref="T:System.Type" /> from the dictionary.
trans-unit.target: 从字典移除具有指定 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 的对象。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the object is successfully found and removed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果成功找到并移除该对象，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的对象的类型。

trans-unit.source: This is the key that is associated with the object.
trans-unit.target: 这是与对象相关联的密钥。

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains the object associated with the specified key, if the key is found; otherwise, the default value for the type of the <c>value</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: 当此方法返回时，如果找到指定的键，则包含与该键关联的对象；否则包含 <c>value</c> 参数的类型默认值。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: 此参数未经初始化即被传递。

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that has the specified type.
trans-unit.target: 获取具有指定类型的对象。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the dictionary contains an object of type <paramref name="T" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果字典包含类型为 <paramref name="T" /> 的对象，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。

trans-unit.source: The type of the object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的对象的类型。

trans-unit.source: The key of the object to get.
trans-unit.target: 要获取的对象的键。

trans-unit.source: When this method returns, contains the object associated with the specified key, if the key is found and the object has the type <c>T</c>; otherwise, the default value for the type of the <c>value</c> parameter.
trans-unit.target: 当此方法返回时，如果找到指定的键，且对象具有类型 <c>T</c>，则包含与该键关联的对象；否则包含 <c>value</c> 参数的类型的默认值。

trans-unit.source: This parameter is passed uninitialized.
trans-unit.target: 此参数未经初始化即被传递。

trans-unit.source: Gets the object that has the specified type and is associated with the specified key.
trans-unit.target: 获取具有指定类型并与指定键相关联的对象。

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the dictionary contains an object with the specified key and the object has the type <paramref name="T" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 如果字典包含具有指定键的对象，且该对象具有类型 <paramref name="T" />，则为 <see langword="true" />；否则为 <see langword="false" />。
